<item>
            <title>[LU-7408] multislot RPC support didn&apos;t declare write for reply_data object</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7408</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For clients with multislot supported, it will call tgt_add_reply_data() update save reply data but this object(extended last_rcvd) is never declared for write. We should add the corresponding code in tgt_txn_start_cb().&lt;/p&gt;</description>
